Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小艾！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你复仇的机会 绮丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是真矢的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去报仇吧 比利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道再生要花多少时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还有最后一手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人想起找爸爸妈妈的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找死人有什么用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能替那些人活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命的记忆会创造未来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸妈妈 还有我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了你的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广登？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晖…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没能写下的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:03:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要由你来写
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 我讨厌这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别丢下我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晖！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑司前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晖…和广登一起走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 一个亲人也保护不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是他留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的责任…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零央
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美三香！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美三香 你是美三香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:04:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 我喘不过气了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三Alvis原来的内核吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为爸爸的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光弘和人类军肯定都会被那个内核控制着攻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没必要承担这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…你并没有明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑 你回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿育的内核正在死亡边缘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你怀着和平的心愿选择了战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好你没事…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么困难的任务 你完成得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢和Mk.Nicht你都保护了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会违背内核的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来了啊 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你选择的道路 我也会选择
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 远见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广登呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把一部分遗体带回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是敌人干的 还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:06:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晖那边我来解释
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晖…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经…不在了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来！远见…前 辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人…这不是真的…阿广…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回家 广登
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定很疼吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后 你可以好好休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么！为什么！为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了 卡农
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的同化现象是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渐渐没有感觉了 不管是热 是冷 还是痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指挥有没有问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.42,0:08:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道什么时候会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们大家要一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天葬礼过后就办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:09:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成人礼啊 我们的成人礼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对沃尔特先生说 让他到岛上来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我就想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道广登平安的消息之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就写个别的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望全世界的人都能知道龙宫岛的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这条命要到头了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你会遇见这架机体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它就将成为你的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫皆城总士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你听到这段话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该已经不在这个世界上了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(Partb)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才交给各位的Alvis访问权限就是各位所肩负的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望各位尊重过去与你们同在之人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相保护当下与你们同在之人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,度过这个苦难的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位正是我们引以为傲的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnMingLiU\fs36\blur3\bord1\1a&H24&\c&HFFFFFF&}— 三天后 —
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海神岛的两个防护罩都已经修复
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没有伪装镜面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过迎击系统状态良好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅶ和Mk.Ⅳ的改装也已经完成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(690,655)}conversion
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时可以出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类军的动向怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大舰队北上 没有回应我们的讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类军拥有流浪者与第三部救世主型
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是十分严重的威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牵牛的情况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据通识者的预测
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它将在24小时内接近地球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 上空的敌人正在阻碍阿育的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的要害就是流浪者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜部队负责对付这个敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大气层外的敌人要怎么对付？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西尾里奈和镝木彗驾驶零式法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运用他们两人的SDP将敌人拖到地上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何SDP在零式上都可以发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个方案在模拟中也是成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类军由我们来对付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有需要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来和人类军作战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们学会的只有人类的可怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人有时会变得十分可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我们仍然应该相信人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城总士 真壁一骑 远见真矢 近藤剑司 近藤咲良 春日井甲洋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立上芹 西尾里奈 镝木彗 御门零央 水镜美三香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会命令你们攻击人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为法芙娜驾驶员 完成你们的使命！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里会成为未来的岔道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你告诉我们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出发了 织姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的可以坐在晖前辈的位置上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会放大你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你要把天上的敌人拖到我面前来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 舞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好跟他们说吧 为了不要后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贡 沟口先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明你们都是为阿广而去了那么危险的地方 我却…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没能完成任务 你怪我们是应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会让广登的战斗白费的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都要平安回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的岛就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全舰进入攻击态势
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为应对与Festum的战斗 禁止与己方舰队以外的对象通信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四次苍穹作战现在开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上空出现敌群
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎击系统全部启动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海面上出现阿撒谢尔型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外部防护罩无法维持
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维持航向 法芙娜部队出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 按训练时做的那样匹配波长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 别老看我的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了之后我会让你看个够的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中精力执行计划 明白没？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:15:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛上的所罗门传来消息 是阿撒谢尔型爬行者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:15:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(970,655)}Crawler
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,执行流浪者歼灭方案！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一至第三部队 全机更新位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零式 启动SDP！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好远
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们休想过去 Festum！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一只！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两只！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三只！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高帕程序 启动！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了没那种程序啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往前冲 我来破坏敌人的力场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一起战斗真开心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真够大的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也就这点能耐么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回归——
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虚无去——!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到你们该待的虚无里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的力场已经瓦解！开始迎击！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉到你的存在了 Festum！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的同化…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼痛我来承担…你集中精神！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰队 距离30单位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有舰只均无法通信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度0 熄灭引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熄灭？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度降为0
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在熄灭引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通信频道开放
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不认为对方会回应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会把话送到！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D岛停下了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是打算拿自己当挡箭牌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜大队去镇压第三Alvis！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他来个两面夹击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是狙击 我们被攻击了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么远的距离居然能打中？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人都没死？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是没打算杀我们…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告系统
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诱导敌人 把他们当掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你的心脏吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下希望就会成长了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,——以我们的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说再见了 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 敌人的力场又恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不攻击D岛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还有利用价值
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是太天真了呢 真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救济之火 任何时候看来都这么美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我下来——！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流浪者居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天上的Mir掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算能打它了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是在玩 来主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你让我们战斗的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受你杀了那么多人的报应吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.84,0:22:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 我也能开爸爸造的救世主型！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样 光弘！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别犹豫 一骑！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是被灌输了自己是人这个观念的——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想得逞！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别挡路——!!
